Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:25.56,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master.}Chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:30.33,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's morning.}Sáng rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:32.42,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Who are you?}Ai vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:37.77,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You must still be half-asleep.}Ngài vẫn còn mơ ngủ nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:41.70,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:42.63,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Vâng.{Yes.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:44.86,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Good morning, young master.}Chào buổi sáng chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.13,0:00:48.33,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I thought you had today off.}Tôi tưởng hôm nay cô nghỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.83,0:00:58.16,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{E-Even so, I can't neglect \Nmy morning duties.}D-Dù là vậy, tôi không thể không làm nhiệm vụ buổi sáng...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:05.63,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Tôi sẽ chuẩn bị bữa sáng.{I'll prepare breakfast right away.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:06.65,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.41,0:01:17.36,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Who was that girl?}Cô gái đó là ai?
