Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:03:02.52,Ep_Title - Sus Maid,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2\pos(610.667,300)}{Episode 8: The Girl With the Purple Eyes}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:04.01,Top,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Pardon me, young master.}Xin thứ lỗi, chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:18.45,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Why is she all dressed up?}Sao cô ấy lại ăn mặc đẹp?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:20.12,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Is she meeting someone?}Đi gặp ai à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:23.45,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's not... a date, is it?!}Không lẽ... hẹn hò?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:28.92,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, are you sure \NI may really take the day off?}Chủ nhân, ngài có chắc là tôi được nghỉ không?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:30.54,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{O-Of course.}D-Dĩ nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:35.18,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's part of a master's job to \Nallow his servants to take breaks.}Chủ nhân thỉnh thoảng cũng\N phải cho người hầu nghỉ ngơi chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.06,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Understood.}Đã rõ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:40.72,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I shall take you up on the offer.}Vậy tôi xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:05.73,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I still have some time until our meeting.}Vẫn còn ít thời gian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:07.42,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What should I do?}Làm gì đây nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:11.27,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Something smells nice.}Mùi gì thơm ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:12.97,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What could it be?}Là gì nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:28.13,Main,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,{Welcome.}Chào mừng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:32.98,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That looks delicious.}Trông ngon quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:37.41,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I think I'll buy some for the young master.}Mình sẽ mua một ít cho chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:41.24,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{He likes sweet bread.}Ngài ấy rất thích bánh ngọt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:43.86,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{These chocolate strawberry krones,}Bánh dâu tây socola này,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:47.49,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{and these seasonal Marron Danishes...}và cả bánh Marron Danishes theo mùa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:49.92,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Croissants are a must-have, too.}Bánh sừng bò cũng ngon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:53.04,Main,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,{Would you like to try a sample?}Quý khách có dùng thử không?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:55.10,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:00.86,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's very delicious.}Nó ngon ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:02.74,Main,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,{I'm glad.}May quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.03,Main,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,{Is something the matter?}Có chuyện gì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:09.49,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{No, it's nothing.}Không, không có gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:22.96,Main,Boy,0,0,0,,{Wait!}Chờ đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:26.12,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,{But I can't wait to show Mom.}Nhưng chị muốn gặp mẹ ngay cơ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:46.51,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I wonder if the young master \Nis doing all right by himself.}Không biết chủ nhân một mình ổn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:49.66,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I hope he's had his meal.}Hi vọng ngài ấy có thể tự dùng bữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.35,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I hope he's not in any trouble.}Chắc không có gì xảy ra đâu nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:55.01,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'm so worried.}Mình lo quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:58.45,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Worrying about your master again?}Lại lo lắng cho chủ nhân à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:05:59.89,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Fujisaki-san.}Fujisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:02.65,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{I apologize for being late.}Xin lỗi vì đến trễ nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:05.63,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Thank you for coming.}Cảm ơn vì đã đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:08.64,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Actually, I'm off duty today, as well.}Không, hôm nay tôi cũng nghỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:10.44,Main,Shop 2,0,0,0,,{Welcome.}Chào mừng quý khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:12.37,Main,Shop 2,0,0,0,,{Have you decided what to order?}Quý khách đã quyết định món gì chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:13.99,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{I'll have what she had.}Cho tôi giống cô ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:15.50,Main,Shop 2,0,0,0,,Vâng ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:24.42,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{I do wonder, though, if you really ought to \Nbe worrying about your master on your day off.}Cơ mà ngay cả ngày nghỉ cô cũng lo cho chủ nhân à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:25.74,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes...}Phải...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:30.70,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Don't you ever get worried \Nabout Gojouin-sama?}Cô không lo cho tiểu thư sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:31.94,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Not at all.}Không hẳn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:36.64,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I see...}Vậy à...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:40.39,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I suppose it must be because \Nof your long-standing bond.}Có lẽ là do mối liên kết sâu đậm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:42.84,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Does it all seem so nice to you?}Cô cảm thấy thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:45.66,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,Hoàn cảnh của chúng ta cũng tương tự nhau mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:47.76,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's very different.}Hoàn toàn khác chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:51.39,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Setting aside the time you've already had,}Không tính việc đã cùng sống với tiểu thư từ lâu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:55.54,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I still haven't fully opened \Nmy young master's heart.}tôi thậm chí còn chưa mở lòng hoàn toàn với chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:57.94,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Even this morning...}Ngay cả sáng nay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:03.98,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{I don't think you need to be so anxious.}Không cần phải vội vã đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:12.29,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You sure have changed, Fujisaki-san.}Cô đã thay đổi rồi nhỉ Fujisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:17.66,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I heard lots of rumors about you \Nduring our time at the academy.}Tôi nghe nhiều tin đồn về cô hồi còn đi học.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:23.62,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That you were the worst student at school, \Nuntil you suddenly changed one day.}Cô từng là một học sinh cá biệt nhất, và đột nhiên thay đổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:30.12,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I thought it was just a rumor at the time, \Nbut having met you again, I'm certain of it.}Tôi cứ nghĩ đó chỉ là tin đồn nhưng giờ thì đã tin nó là thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:35.18,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You must have changed when \Nyou met Gojouin-sama.}Hẳn cô thay đổi từ khi gặp tiểu thư Gojouin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:39.20,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{The air around you is very tender.}Bầu không khí giữa hai người cũng thật ấm áp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:40.56,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Would you please stop?}Làm ơn dừng lại đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:43.09,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{This is embarrassing for me.}Xấu hổ lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:44.86,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I-I'm sorry.}X-Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:50.32,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Anyway, I truly admire the two of you.}Tôi thực sự ngưỡng mộ hai người đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:54.51,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{How can I become like you two?}Làm sao để giống hai người?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:08:00.36,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{To me, the two of you \Nseem far more admirable.}Với tôi thì hai người mới là toả sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:05.32,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{The young lady is very interested \Nin your relationship, as well.}Tiểu thư cũng rất tò mò về quan hệ giữa cô với chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:08.21,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{But, well...}Nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:11.46,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{If I were to give you any advice,}Nếu phải đưa ra lời khuyên,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:16.26,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{I would say that what's important is \Nfor you to open your own heart.}thì tôi cho rằng việc mở lòng là rất quan trọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:24.40,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{I'm sure your master will\N open his heart to you then.}Tôi chắc chủ nhân cũng sẽ mở lòng với cô thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:28.59,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I don't know if I can do it.}Tôi không biết mình có làm được không...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:08:59.82,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{When we were at the academy,}Hồi còn ở trường,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:03.62,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{you seemed to be burdened with a \Ndifferent kind of loneliness than mine.}cô dường như đang chịu \Nmột sự cô đơn nào đó còn lớn hơn tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:09.29,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{You had such an \Nunapproachable air about you,}Xung quanh cô mang bầu không khí không thể tiếp cận,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:11.85,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{and yet you've come to talk to me.}vậy mà cô vẫn lại nói chuyện với tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:16.89,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{I think you've already begun to change.}Tôi nghĩ cô cũng đã thay đổi rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:22.05,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Excuse me.}Xin phép.
