Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:26.95,sign_13327_95_Tsukasa_,Text,0,0,0,,{Tsukasa}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:27.24,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Hurry! Hurry up and show me \Nthe picture you took with her!}Nhanh cho tôi xem ảnh hai người chụp chung đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:31.52,sign_13406_97_Give_me_details_,Text,0,0,0,,{Give me details of what you talked\N about with the maid when \Nyou get home!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:31.58,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Give me details of what you talked \Nabout with the maid when you get home!}Khi nào về nhớ kể lại mọi chuyện đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:32.83,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Was it about romance?}Có lãng mạn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:32.64,sign_13517_98_Was_it_about_rom,Text,0,0,0,,{Was it about romance?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:34.71,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I want to join, too!}Tôi cũng muốn tham gia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:34.71,sign_13545_99_I_want_to_join__,Text,0,0,0,,{I want to join, too!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:36.48,Top Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{If you're talking about romance,}Nếu nói về lãng mạn,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:39.54,Top Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I have some questions I'd \Nlike you to ask her for me.}tôi có vài câu hỏi cần cô hỏi cô ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:39.14,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What is it?}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:42.51,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{I apologize. The young lady is calling for me.}Không có gì, chủ nhân gọi tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.19,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{I must be going.}Tôi phải đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:49.39,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{So you do worry about Gojouin-sama.}Vậy là cô lo cho tiểu thư nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:55.45,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{I-In any case, I enjoyed talking \Nabout old times today.}T-Tóm lại cảm ơn vì hôm nay đã ôn lại chuyện cũ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:00.64,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{You haven't talked to your \Nmaster yet, have you?}Cô vẫn chưa nói cho chủ nhân nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:06.78,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{I think you have what it \Ntakes to tell him now.}Tôi nghĩ cô nên nói ngay đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:18.37,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Talked?}Nói chuyện?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:19.84,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Talked about what?}Chuyện gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:23.76,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I couldn't help but follow her here.}Mình đã tò mò và bám theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:28.74,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Is Lilith hiding something from me?}Lilith đang giấu gì mình sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:30.58,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Something I don't know about?}Gì đó mà mình không biết?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:35.37,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,{Oh, dear.}Chà chà.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.92,0:10:46.45,Top Italics,Mom,0,0,0,,{So that I can shine by your side}Mẹ sẽ luôn toả sáng bên cạnh con
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:53.11,Top Italics,Mom,0,0,0,,{In the future that is yet to come}Tuy tương lai bất định
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:11:02.42,Top Italics,Mom,0,0,0,,{I continue to search}Nhưng mẹ vẫn sẽ tìm kiếm
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:12.69,Top Italics,Mom,0,0,0,,{And walk on beyond the rainbow}Và bước cùng con dưới ánh cầu vồng
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:20.78,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, I've returned home.}Chủ nhân, tôi về rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.98,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I bought lots of gifts.}Tôi mua nhiều quà lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.03,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Is something the matter?}Có chuyện gì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:31.72,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Your eyes seem even more intense than usual.}Ngài có vẻ dữ dội hơn mọi khi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:35.03,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Is there something you \Nwant to tell me about?}Có chuyện gì cô cần nói không?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:37.58,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What is the "talk"?}Chuyện đó là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:39.97,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{The "talk"?}Chuyện đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:42.08,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That's right, the talk.}Phải, chuyện đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:45.22,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Which talk are you talking about?}Chuyện nào vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:46.67,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Something important!}Chuyện quan trọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.25,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Important?}Quan trọng?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.05,0:11:54.66,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'll be making Hamburg \Nsteaks for dinner tonight.}Hôm nay tôi sẽ làm món Hamburg.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:55.76,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{No!}Không phải!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:58.11,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Would that not be to your liking?}Ngài không thích ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:00.12,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'll make something else, then.}Vậy tôi sẽ làm món khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:01.44,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That's not it.}Không phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:02.80,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I like Hamburg steaks.}Tôi thích Hamburg.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:06.52,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I like them really juicy.}Và thích nó phải mọng nước.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:09.28,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Understood.}Đã rõ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:10.86,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{No, I mean...}Không phải!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:15.92,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Isn't there something more important \Nthat you're keeping from me?}Có chuyện quan trọng bí mật\N gì đó cô không nói với tôi không?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:18.95,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{An important secret?}Chuyện bí mật quan trọng?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:23.18,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You were talking to the Gojouin \Nbutler today, weren't you?}Hôm nay cô đã nói chuyện với quản gia của Gojouin nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:25.31,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{How did you...}Sao ngài biết...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:31.36,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Were you following me?}Ngài theo dõi tôi sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:32.32,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.17,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I couldn't help but be curious.}Tôi quá tò mò nên đi theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:39.58,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You were dressed cuter than \Never when you left the house.}Cô ăn mặc dễ thương và rời khỏi nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:43.79,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're always in your maid \Noutfit around me. It's not fair.}Cô lúc nào cũng mặc đồ hầu gái trước mặt tôi, thật bất công.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:46.34,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Who were you meeting? Where?}Cô gặp ai? Ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:48.52,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Why wasn't it with me?}Tại sao không phải là tôi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:49.70,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master...}Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:54.71,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{And you were discussing telling me\N }{\i1}{something}{\i0}{, and it sounded important.}Và cô đang nói gì đó về tôi với vẻ mặt nghiêm trọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:00.56,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Sorry.}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:07.50,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Lilith, when she said something \Nabout telling me something...}Lilith, cái chuyện cô cần nói với tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:11.22,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Was it about how you met me in the past?}Có phải là về quá khứ của tôi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:15.81,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{How did you know?}Sao ngài biết?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:21.37,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I remembered a little bit \Nabout when I was little.}Tôi đã nhớ hồi còn nhỏ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:25.63,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{About the girl my parents \Nbrought to this mansion.}Về một cô gái mà ba mẹ tôi đã đưa về.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:29.88,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She looked nothing like she does now...}Tuy khác hoàn toàn với cô lúc này...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:41.37,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{But that girl was you, wasn't she?}Nhưng cô gái đó là cô nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:46.58,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That song, too.}Bài hát đó nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:50.21,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You sang it for me in my mother's place.}Cô hát bài hát đó thay cho mẹ tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:52.07,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Isn't that right?}Phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:56.42,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:14:00.51,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Why did you keep something \Nso important from me?!}Tại sao lại giấu chuyện đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:03.24,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Because...}Vì...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:08.23,Flashback - Sus Maid,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{What's important is for you \Nto open your own heart.}Quan trọng là cô phải mở lòng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:15.41,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You'll think I'm an awful \Nperson if I tell you.}Nếu tôi nói ra thì chủ nhân có nghĩ tôi là\N người kinh khủng không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:18.70,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{In fact, you might come to hate me.}Và ngài có thể sẽ ghét tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:19.90,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{No, I won't!}Không bao giờ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:26.61,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I thought I should tell \Nyou in the beginning.}Đáng ra tôi phải nói ngay từ đầu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:32.05,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{But I wanted you to remember it on your own.}Nhưng tôi muốn ngài tự nhớ lại...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:37.06,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What if, even after I told you, \Nyou still didn't remember?}Dù có nói ra mà ngài không nhớ thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:42.15,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That thought kept me from bringing it up.}Thế nên tôi không dám nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:44.76,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I remembered.}Tôi nhớ chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:47.02,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I remembered, Lilith.}Tôi nhớ mà Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:52.51,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm going to remember everything \Nabout you that I've forgotten, too.}Tôi sẽ nhớ tất cả mọi thứ về Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:56.11,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{So don't look so sad.}Thế nên đừng buồn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.20,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master?}Chủ nhân?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:25.44,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Where has he gone?}Ngài ấy đi đâu rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:32.89,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master?}Chủ nhân?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:35.25,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What are you up to this early in the morning?}Ngài làm gì dậy sớm vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:37.20,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Lilith. Perfect timing.}Lilith à? Đúng lúc lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:38.85,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Give me your hand.}Đưa tay cô đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:40.60,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{My hand?}Tay tôi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:49.55,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Y-Young master, this is...}C-Chủ nhân, đây là...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.29,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That doesn't work, huh?}Không được à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:54.88,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{D-Doesn't work?}K-Không được?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:56.62,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's not that it doesn't work...}Không phải là không được...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:58.66,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I mean, it doesn't, but...}Ý tôi là không được...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:04.07,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I thought I might remember more about \Nyou if I did something I did that day.}Cứ tưởng làm thế sẽ nhớ ra chuyện tôi đã làm ngày hôm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:06.85,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That day...}Ngày hôm đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:14.49,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master...}Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:19.26,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, we should get ready now.}Chủ nhân, chúng ta nên chuẩn bị thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:21.03,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You'll be late for school.}Ngài sẽ trễ học đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.03,0:16:22.27,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Shoot!}Chết!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:23.55,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{We have to hurry, Lilith.}Chúng ta phải nhanh lên.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:25.15,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Let's continue when I get home.}Khi nào tôi về rồi tiếp tục.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:25.91,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Right.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:31.21,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Continue?}Tiếp tục?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:41.05,Main,Student A,0,0,0,,{Good morning.}Chào buổi sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.97,Main,Student B,0,0,0,,{Good morning.}Chào buổi sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:45.25,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Morning, Gojouin.}Chào cậu Gojouin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:47.18,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,C-Chào cậu.{G-Good morning.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:51.35,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Has something good\N happened to Yuuri-san?}Có chuyện gì tốt xảy ra à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:03.37,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I don't want it to wilt.}Mình không muốn nó héo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:04.92,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I think I'll make it a bookmark.}Ép khô làm thẻ đọc sách vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.58,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,{All right, then...}Rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:21.33,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,{How about we start taking answers \Nfrom the back row today?}Bắt đầu từ hàng sau nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:25.93,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Yuuri-san!}Yuuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:29.72,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Could it be that you've made some \Nkind of progress with your maid?}Có chuyện gì tiến triển với chị hầu gái hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:33.13,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{How disgraceful of me!}Tớ thật thất lễ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:35.54,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I only meant to watch from afar, but...}Đáng ra chỉ nên đứng quan sát từ xa thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:37.11,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I want the goods!}Nhưng tớ muốn có tư liệu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:38.43,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Goods?}Tư liệu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:46.48,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{O-Oh, it's just that you seem to \Nbe in a good mood today, so...}À không, cơ mà sáng nay trông cậu có vẻ vui, nên...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:50.56,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I thought maybe you'd made some progress \Nin your relationship with your maid.}Tớ nghĩ có gì đó tiến triển giữa cậu với chị hầu gái.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:53.62,Flashback - Sus Maid,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{You're in love.}Cậu đang yêu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:58.51,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I was so busy trying to remember \Nabout Lilith, I'd totally forgotten.}Mình đã quá tập trung vào kí ức với Lilith mà quên mất!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:01.13,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{So something really did happen?}Vậy có chuyện gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:02.99,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Please tell me about it!}Hãy kể tớ nghe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:05.32,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Wh-What do you want to know?}C-Cậu muốn biết gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:07.17,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{It can be anything!}Bất cứ thứ gì!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:09.14,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Anything that happened with the maid.}Mọi chuyện với chị hầu gái!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:14.30,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{We slept together.}Bọn tớ đã ngủ cùng nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:20.87,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Ngủ cùng nhau...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:26.97,Italics,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Yuuri-san's climbed the stairs to adulthood.}Yuuri đã leo lên nấc thang người trưởng thành...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:32.21,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{So when did you confess?}Vậy tỏ tình khi nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.59,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Confess?}Tỏ tình?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:43.00,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{D-Don't tell me you s-s-s-s-s-s-s-s-slept \Nwith her without even confessing to her!}Đ-Đừng nói là n-n-ngủ với nhau nhưng chưa tỏ tình đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.39,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{You've gotten things in the wrong order!}Như vậy là hơi sai quy trình!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:46.76,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What do you mean, confess?}Cơ mà tỏ tình gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:49.44,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Confess your love, of course!}Nói cảm xúc của mình cho cô ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:52.25,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's not love or romance or anything...}Mấy cái như tình yêu này nọ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:54.77,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm just really suspicious of Lilith.}Tớ chỉ tò mò về Lilith thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:56.60,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That's why I want to get to know her better.}Thế nên muốn biết rõ về cô ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:58.03,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,Cậu lại thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:18:59.64,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{You realize it, don't you?}Cậu cũng nhận ra rồi mà nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:04.09,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{That you're in love with your maid.}Rằng mình cực kì yêu chị ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:09.71,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Me? With Lilith?}Tớ? Với Lilith?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:10.83,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{That's right!}Phải đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:14.36,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,Tò mò đến độ muốn biết rõ về đối phương.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:17.13,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{That's because you love her.}Đó là vì cậu yêu chị ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:26.94,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{So the reason I've been wanting to \Nlearn more about her all this time...}Vậy lý do mình muốn hiểu rõ về Lilith...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:32.57,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{This feeling I thought was suspicion...}Và cảm xúc mà mình nghĩ nó đáng nghi này...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.44,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Yuuri-san?}Yuuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:46.10,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Thanks, Gojouin.}Cảm ơn Gojouin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:48.06,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I have to go!}Tớ phải đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:51.48,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Wait, please! I want to go, too!}Khoan, tớ đi nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:56.49,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Young lady, how long are you \Ngoing to keep me waiting?}Tiểu thư, cô còn định để tôi chờ đến khi nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:58.56,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{You have lessons today.}Hôm nay vẫn còn giờ học thêm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:01.95,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{But it was just getting good!}Nhưng mọi chuyện chỉ mới tốt lên thôi mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:05.76,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I see.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:07.08,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{So that's why!}Đó là lý do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:11.81,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I was always so anxious over \Nwhat I didn't know about Lilith.}Mình đã luôn lo lắng vì không hiểu gì về Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:16.03,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Lilith was anxious, too,}Lilith cũng vậy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:19.18,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{that I might not remember her.}không phải là vì mình không nhớ về Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:22.12,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{And I've thought she was\N suspicious this whole time.}Và những điều đáng nghi về Lilith...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:23.73,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Ngay cả bây giờ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:25.93,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I have to tell her.}Mình phải nói cho cô ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:27.17,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Right now!}Ngay lúc này!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:36.48,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I...}Tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:39.38,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm...}Tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:42.36,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{in love with you.}đã yêu cô mất rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:46.71,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I love you so much that}Tôi đã yêu cô quá nhiều
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:48.75,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{even when you're cleaning, my eyes follow you.}đến độ mỗi khi cô quét nhà là tôi không thể rời mắt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:53.20,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I love your voice when \Nyou wake me each morning...}Tôi yêu giọng nói cô đánh thức tôi mỗi sáng...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:56.77,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Your gentle voice when you sing me lullabies...}Giọng hát ru dịu dàng đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:21:01.56,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{The way you buy me things, \Neven on your days off...}Những món cô mua cho tôi dù đang trong ngày nghỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:05.74,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I love how your smile is \Nlike the sun shining on me.}Tôi yêu nụ cười toả sáng của cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:08.46,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Tôi {I love your amused laughter.}yêu tiếng cười khúc khích của cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:12.69,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I love your beautiful eyes that \Ndraw me in with their sparkle.}Tôi yêu ánh mắt lấp lánh hút hồn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:19.86,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I love everything about you.}Tôi yêu tất cả về cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:31.56,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, I...}Chủ nhân, tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:39.16,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,Nãy giờ... chỉ toàn nói mồm thôi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:40.50,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Wh-Who are you?}C-Cô là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:44.06,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I have some business with that maid there.}Tôi có việc với hầu gái đằng kia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:49.87,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Lilith, leave this mansion and \Nreturn to my place at once!}Lilith, mau rời khỏi đây và quay lại chỗ tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:51.34,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Wh-What?!}C-Cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:54.17,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Natsume...
